{"tid":1072244,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"水貨客着5件衫　夥小學生穿梭闖關","createTime":"2019-03-22T01:50:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-22T03:32:15.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0ceca450b9ecd4c468a4270384f1e1a7bf48c7a9","tid":1072244,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T01:50:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190322/photo/bkn-20190322050035638-0322_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190322090028\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190322%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190322050035638-0322_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190322090028&h=d5730154&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近日天水圍水貨又再死灰復燃。東網連日直擊，大批水貨客盤據深圳灣口岸，輪流等高峰期闖關，有水貨客穿着5件衫闖關，又有學生穿着新鞋新衣北上，送貨後即換回舊衣舊鞋返港，再走一轉。立法會議員促內地海關及香港警方加強執法，杜絕區內水貨活動，減少影響民生。 <br />\n<br />\n「開門呀，開門呀！」日前黃昏6時許，1名大媽在港鐵天水圍站附近，經1輛輕型貨車接載及落車後，一度以為司機駛離，狂拍車尾叫嚷着司機打開尾門，原來車尾箱載着多袋貨物準備「走」往深圳，而該批五名同行水貨兵團中，包括兩名身穿校服的中小學女生。 <br />\n<br />\n至7時許過關人潮高峰，中學女生「打頭陣」混入人群過關，之後2名男女亦先後穿上新鞋及羽絨外套相繼過關。東網記者見該女生過關後，即到附近石壆上換回舊鞋，並小心翼翼將新鞋放入背囊。同夥另一男人過關後亦走到附近換回拖鞋，並將新鞋放入膠袋，2人及後將貨物交予1名攜着紅白藍膠袋來取貨的女子。另有大媽及小學女生則以「母女檔」闖關，「女兒」換上新鞋過關後。約晚上9時，2人將多袋貨物送抵深圳。 <br />\n<br />\n在深圳灣口岸的水貨客不少將水貨「上身」扮自用。記者曾目擊一名男子，過關前先脫下舊衣，從行李中取出多件新衫拆袋，先後穿上3件短袖及1件長袖襯衫，再加1件外套，在溫暖的天氣下身穿5件衣服，與同黨一同過關。 <br />\n<br />\n天耀邨巴士總站是水貨活動活躍範圍，日前下午約4時，東網記者直擊一批約10人的水貨客，從貨車卸下數十袋水貨後，各人取走兩袋步行至附近天耀邨內分貨。水貨客乘人流高峰期闖關，其中一名水貨大媽過關後，將兩袋貨交予接貨的女子，隨即趕返香港「走多轉」，20分鐘後又返回深圳。 <br />\n<br />\n「要將啲貨着上身，係因為『衰過』有底，大陸海關一碌張卡就知，如果發現係新貨，就要佢哋退貨，或者打稅。」從事中港水貨活動多年的明哥（化名）指「走」衣服及日用品水貨的「利錢」不高，以1名水貨客走2轉計，最多賺百多元。 <br />\n<br />\n身兼元朗區議員的立法會議員陸頌雄表示，最有效打擊水貨活動始終是內地海關加緊執法，而香港警方亦要加強在水貨活動活躍點巡查及疏導工作。 <br />\n<br />\n警方由本周二（19日）起一連2日在深圳灣口岸進行打擊水貨行動，先後拘捕7男1女，共檢獲5萬港元水貨。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190322/photo/bkn-20190322050035638-0322_00822_001_02p.jpg?20190322090028\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190322%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190322050035638-0322_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20190322090028&h=8d6da87c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n貨車連人帶貨送到港鐵天水圍站附近。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190322/photo/bkn-20190322050035638-0322_00822_001_03p.jpg?20190322090028\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190322%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190322050035638-0322_00822_001_03p.jpg%3F20190322090028&h=0c48cd5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一行5人水貨兵團，包括2名中小學女生。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190322/photo/bkn-20190322050035638-0322_00822_001_04p.jpg?20190322090028\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190322%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190322050035638-0322_00822_001_04p.jpg%3F20190322090028&h=3d50fa2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n抵達深圳灣口岸後，各人隨即換上新鞋。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190322/photo/bkn-20190322050035638-0322_00822_001_05p.jpg?20190322090028\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190322%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190322050035638-0322_00822_001_05p.jpg%3F20190322090028&h=bc759f0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中學女生身穿及手挽2件新外套，並穿上新波鞋過關。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190322/photo/bkn-20190322050035638-0322_00822_001_06p.jpg?20190322090028\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190322%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190322050035638-0322_00822_001_06p.jpg%3F20190322090028&h=e46b3623&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n過關後，即走到一旁換回舊鞋，並小心翼翼將新鞋放入背囊。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190322/photo/bkn-20190322050035638-0322_00822_001_07p.jpg?20190322090028\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190322%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190322050035638-0322_00822_001_07p.jpg%3F20190322090028&h=654e5304&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n水貨客換上新鞋及羽絨外套。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190322/photo/bkn-20190322050035638-0322_00822_001_08p.jpg?20190322090028\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190322%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190322050035638-0322_00822_001_08p.jpg%3F20190322090028&h=865b58cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n水貨客最後再披上長袖外套，一共穿上5件衣服，同行女子亦忙着穿上新衣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190322/photo/bkn-20190322050035638-0322_00822_001_09p.jpg?20190322090028\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190322%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190322050035638-0322_00822_001_09p.jpg%3F20190322090028&h=077e3dea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在深圳灣口岸附近多處均有水貨活動，不少人過關後忙於交貨及執貨。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190322/bkn-20190322050035638-0322_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190322%2Fbkn-20190322050035638-0322_00822_001.html&d=nGD0VYfdVRVKlmm%2FccroEy9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=e820b190\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190322/bkn-20190322050035638-0322_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"d865e9dc63d6d2a1fecb454d91c32c4ec5bd1254","tid":1072244,"uid":152476,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T02:00:59.000Z","msg":"支那無衫買？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f83956c3786ef4bae6211ebe8fd78655dab8172","tid":1072244,"uid":44309,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T02:02:12.000Z","msg":"要講幾多次呀？係 走私， 唔係水貨。"},{"pid":"6ea097d3780f696f425ff151a2f7581c40bf9894","tid":1072244,"uid":57844,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T02:03:39.000Z","msg":"攪撚到好似70年代咁呀? 衫都要走私??"},{"pid":"905a3671f452fe818848567726fc139194e70bc7","tid":1072244,"uid":57844,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d865e9dc63d6d2a1fecb454d91c32c4ec5bd1254","tid":1072244,"uid":152476,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T02:00:59.000Z","msg":"支那無衫買？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T02:04:08.000Z","msg":"咪係, 香港衫咪又係淘寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2406ea0c20e8f62063ccc540c5927a78413a099","tid":1072244,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T02:46:40.000Z","msg":"利用小朋友 係支那人先做得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9013bfb8725ea8015e879d8cc3a4e88094b377c1","tid":1072244,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ea097d3780f696f425ff151a2f7581c40bf9894","tid":1072244,"uid":57844,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T02:03:39.000Z","msg":"攪撚到好似70年代咁呀? 衫都要走私??"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T02:49:37.000Z","msg":"以前真係一窮二白就話接濟<br />\n而家日日講強國勃起又係咁<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d94c65c42f01fb8c74189361224afa43317ee81a","tid":1072244,"uid":212535,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T03:32:15.000Z","msg":"大陸人唔相信外國公司會賣真進口貨，咪入香港嘅外國貨囉<br />\n<br />\n事實上啲外國公司都係掛個名賣大陸制嘢，邊間就唔指名道姓啦，費事畀人清算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}